      "title": "Massive protest begins in Kelani",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thousands of students started a protest in Kelani demanding the immediate resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Thousands of students gathered outside Kelani University and marched towards Colombo Fort demanding the resignation of the President and Prime Minister.",
        "Meanwhile, the students are expected to stay overnight and participate in the nationwide protest tomorrow."
      ],
